title: Hour 1 -Stanley Cup Playoff Goals, Madden Cover, LIV Tour

Dan dissects the impact of the LIV Tour on the PGA, addresses the spate of goals in the Stanley Cup Playoffs, and speculates on the latest Madden Football cover image.
